# System Architecture - Force-Directed Graph

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[User Browser] -->|HTTP Request| B[Next.js Frontend]
    B -->|REST API| C[FastAPI Backend]
    C -->|HTTPS| D[OpenAlex API]
    C -->|Graph Analysis| E[NetworkX]
    E -->|Communities & Metrics| C
    D -->|Papers + References| C
    C -->|JSON Response| B
    B -->|Render| F[react-force-graph-2d]
    F -->|Interactive Visualization| A

    style A fill:#F5F5F5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style B fill:#FF4400,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#FFF
    style C fill:#FF4400,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#FFF
    style D fill:#F5F5F5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style E fill:#F5F5F5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style F fill:#F5F5F5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
```

**说明**:
- 橙色 (#FF4400): 核心服务（Next.js, FastAPI）
- 灰白色 (#F5F5F5): 外部依赖和库
